[[Comberbach]] is a [[civil parish]] in [[Cheshire West and Chester]], England.   Apart from the village of Comberbach, the parish is entirely rural, and contains six buildings that are recorded in the [[National Heritage List for England]] as designated [[listed building]]s.  The buildings are all domestic or related to farming.

